ams of the [[Premier League]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/eu-referendum-premier-league-clubs-back-remain-brexit-vote-what-happens-to-football-teams-a7091201.html|title=All 20 of the Premier League teams have come out in support of Remain|date=20 June 2016|accessdate=23 June 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Quaker Council for European Affairs]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Around Europe|journal=Quaker Council for European Affairs|date=January\u2013March 2016|issue=366|url=http://www.qcea.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Around-Europe-366-JanMar2015-online1.pdf|accessdate=10 March 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Royal College of Midwives]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Royal College of Midwives supportive of Britain's EU Membership|date=18 April 2016|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/apr/18/royal-college-of-midwives-supportive-of-britains-eu-membership|accessdate=19 April 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Royal Society for the Protection of Birds]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/jun/02/rspb-wwf-urge-vote-remain-eu-referendum-protect-uk-wildlife|title=RSPB and WWF urge backers to vote to stay in EU to protect UK wildlife |accessdate=3 June 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Russell Group]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.russellgroup.ac.uk/policy/policy-documents/eu-membership-and-the-effectiveness-of-uk-science/|title=Evidence to the Lords Science and Technology Committee inquiry on the EU|publisher=Russell Group|date=20 November 2015|accessdate=1 March 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Society of Motor Manufacturers and Traders]]<ref name=\"Vauxhall\"/>\n*[[Universities UK]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.universitiesuk.ac.uk/highereducation/Pages/UniversityleadersvoicesupportforEUmembership.aspx|title=University leaders voice support for EU membership|publisher=[[Universities UK]]|date=20 February 2016|accessdate=1 March 2016|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305093300/http://www.universitiesuk.ac.uk/highereducation/Pages/UniversityleadersvoicesupportforE