ffatt]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], mathematician\n*Sir [[Stephen O'Rahilly]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Clinical Biochemistry and Medicine\n*[[Ketan J. Patel|KJ Patel]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], molecular biologist\n*[[Karalyn Patterson]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], psychologist\n*[[Tim Pedley|Timothy Pedley]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], mathematician\n*Sir [[Hugh Pelham]], cell biologist\n*Sir [[Bruce Ponder]], cancer researcher\n*[[Michael Proctor (academic)|Michael Proctor]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Astrophysical Fluid Dynamics\n*[[John A. Pyle|John Pyle]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], director of the Centre for Atmospheric Science\n*[[Randy Read|Randy J. Read]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Protein Crystallography\n*[[Martin Rees]], Baron Rees, [[Astronomer Royal]] and former [[President of the Royal Society]]\n*Sir [[Trevor W. Robbins]], scientist and former president of the [[British Neuroscience Association]]\n*[[David Ron]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Cellular Pathophysiology\n*[[Ekhard Salje|Eckhard K.H Salje]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Mineralogy and Petrology\n*[[Jeremy Sanders|Jeremy K. M. Sanders]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Chemistry\n*[[Patricia Simpson|Pat Simpson]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Comparative Embryology\n*[[Henning Sirringhaus]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Electron Device Physics\n*[[Geoffrey L. Smith]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], virologist\n*[[Maria Grazia Spillantini]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Molecular Neurology\n*Sir [[Peter Swinnerton-Dyer]], mathematician\n*[[Simon Tavar\u00e9]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Cancer Research\n*[[John Clayton Taylor|John C Taylor]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], mathematical physicist\n*Dame [[Jean Thomas (biochemist)|Jean Thomas]], scientist and President of the [[Royal Society of Biology]]\n*[[Roger C. Thomas|Roger Thomas]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], physiologist\n*[[John A. Todd (biologist)|John Todd]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Medical Genetics\n*[[Paul Townsend]], [[ForMemRS|FRS]], Professor of Theoretical Physics\n