bury and Yate)\n* [[Tom Tugendhat]] (Tonbridge and Malling)\n* [[Tania Mathias]] (Twickenham)\n* [[Alun Cairns]] (Vale of Glamorgan)\n* [[David Mowat]] (Warrington South)\n* [[Graham Evans]] (Weaver Vale)\n* [[Steve Brine]] (Winchester)\n* [[Guto Bebb]] (Aberconwy)\n* [[Nick Herbert]] (Arundel and South Downs)\n* [[Damian Green]] (Ashford)\n* [[David Lidington]] (Aylesbury)\n* [[Victoria Prentis]] (Banbury)\n* [[Mark Lancaster]] (North East Milton Keynes)<ref name=MK>{{cite news|url=http://www.miltonkeynes.co.uk/news/local/tory-mps-split-over-vote-to-stay-in-the-european-union-1-7230216|title=Tory MPs split over vote to stay in the European Union|date=24 February 2016|newspaper=[[Milton Keynes Citizen]]|accessdate=26 February 2016}}</ref>\n* [[Maria Miller]] (Basingstoke)\n* [[Ben Howlett]] (Bath)\n* [[Jane Ellison]] (Battersea)\n* [[Dominic Grieve]] (Beaconsfield)\n* [[David Evennett]] (Bexleyheath and Crayford)\n* [[Paul Maynard]] (Blackpool North and Cleveleys)\n* [[Nick Gibb]] (Bognor Regis and Littlehampton)\n* [[Matt Warman]] (Boston and Skegness)\n* [[Tobias Ellwood]] (Bournemouth East)\n* [[Eric Pickles]] (Brentwood and Ongar)\n* [[Simon Kirby]] (Brighton Kemptown)\n* [[Keith Simpson (politician)|Keith Simpson]] (Broadland)\n* [[Bob Neill]] (Bromley and Chislehurt)\n* [[Sajid Javid]] (Bromsgrove)\n* [[Anna Soubry]] (Broxtowe)\n* [[Andrew Griffiths (politician)|Andrew Griffiths]] (Burton)\n* [[Jo Churchill]] (Bury St Edmunds)\n* [[Craig Whittaker]] (Calder Valley)\n* [[Craig Williams (politician)|Craig Williams]] (Cardiff North)\n* [[Simon Hart]] (Carmarthen West and South Pembrokeshire)\n* [[John Stevenson (British politician)|John Stevenson]] (Carlisle)\n* [[Dan Poulter]] (Central Suffolk and North Ipswich)\n* [[Edward Argar]] (Charnwood)\n* [[Simon Burns]] (Chelmsford)\n* [[Greg Hands]] (Chelsea and Fulham)\n* [[Michelle Donelan]] (Chippenham)\n* [[Mark Field]] (Cities of London and Westminster)\n* [[Edward Timpson]] (Crewe and Nantwich)\n* [[Gavin Barwell