ons/a|title=Britain's unions}}</ref>\n*[[Communication Workers Union (UK)|Communication Workers Union]]<ref>{{cite tweet|user=CWUnews|author=The CWU|number=724561562472714240|date=25 April 2016|title=BREAKING \u2013 CWU conference votes overwhelmingly to recommended a REMAIN vote in the #EUref #CWU16|accessdate=26 April 2016|archivedate=31 May 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531032314/http://www.cwu.org/media/news/2016/april/25/dave-ward-makes-call-to-stay-in-the-eu-tent-fighting-for-workers-rights/|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Dave Ward makes call to stay in the EU tent fighting for workers rights|url=http://www.cwu.org/media/news/2016/april/25/dave-ward-makes-call-to-stay-in-the-eu-tent-fighting-for-workers-rights/|website=CWU.org|accessdate=26 April 2016|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531032314/http://www.cwu.org/media/news/2016/april/25/dave-ward-makes-call-to-stay-in-the-eu-tent-fighting-for-workers-rights/|archivedate=31 May 2016}}</ref>\n*Community<ref name=\"tuc.org.uk\"/><ref name=\"auto4\"/><ref name=\"patrika.co\"/><ref name=\"tuc.org.uk1\"/>\n*[[Equity (trade union)|Equity]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestage.co.uk/news/2016/eu-referendum-equity-and-mu-back-remain-campaign/|title=EU referendum: Equity and MU back remain campaign|date=8 April 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Fire Brigades Union]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fbu.org.uk/news/2016/05/12/firefighters-vote-remain-european-union|title= Firefighters vote to remain in the European Union|accessdate=12 May 2016|website=[[Fire Brigades Union]]|date= 12 May 2016}}</ref>\n*[[GMB (trade union)|GMB]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2016/feb/15/gmb-union-backs-campaign-for-uk-to-remain-in-eu|title=GMB union backs campaign for UK to remain in EU|author=Rowena Mason|work=The Guardian}}</ref>\n*[[Musicians' Union (UK)|Musicians' Union]]<ref name=\"tuc.org.uk\"/><ref name=\"auto4\"/><ref name=\"patrika.co\"/><ref name=\"tuc.org.uk1