ewoman.co.uk/laura-perrins-why-i-am-voting-to-leave-the-eu/|title=Laura Perrins: Why I am voting to Leave the EU \u2013 The Conservative Woman|website=conservativewoman.co.uk}}</ref>\n*[[Mike Read]], disc jockey<ref name=\"auto6\"/>\n*[[Jeff Rense]], radio host and conspiracy theorist.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bl5cSL4IpIY|title=YouTube|via=YouTube}}</ref>\n*[[Tommy Robinson (activist)|Tommy Robinson]], political activist and former leader of the [[English Defence League]]<ref>{{cite tweet|user=TRobinsonNewEra|author=Tommy Robinson \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7|number=729359856885485568|date=8 May 2016|title=Vote to leave #Brexit}}</ref>\n*[[Ben Shapiro]], political commentator<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailywire.com/news/6885/4-myths-about-brexit-and-3-reasons-its-good-idea-ben-shapiro|title=4 Myths About Brexit, And 3 Reasons It's A Good Idea|date=23 June 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Paul Staines]], political blogger\n*[[George Galloway]], broadcaster and former Labour/[[Respect Party|Respect]] MP.<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.politicshome.com/news/uk/social-affairs/politics/news/58879/george-galloway-why-im-backing-brexit |title = George Galloway: Why I'm backing Brexit|date = 7 February 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Anthony Worrall Thompson]], restaurateur and celebrity chef<ref>{{Citation|last=BBC Newsnight|title='I'm a proud Brit': Antony Worrall Thompson \u2013 BBC Newsnight|date=22 June 2016|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wPRfa-QrKE0|accessdate=22 June 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Anne Marie Waters]], political activist.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IlxILR0m8nM|title=Anne Marie Waters recalls how she felt on BREXIT night|last=Gravitahn|date=2 April 2017|via=YouTube}}</ref>\n*[[Paul Joseph Watson]], YouTube personality<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5XKJ2mcdVmQ|title=Brexit: Dawn of a Populist Uprising|last=Paul Joseph Watson|date=24 June 2016|via=YouTube}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==Officially endorse neither side==\n===Government==