ssue&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Ozuma]] Anime Interview with Tetsuya Kakihara''\n*''Kiramune Music Festival'' Official Pamphlet&nbsp;\u2013 Released: March 2012<ref>{{Cite web|publisher=Kiramune|title=''Kiramune Music Festival'' Official Pamphlet: Tetsuya Kakihara|url=http://www.e-fanclub.com/kirafes2012/index_cart.asp|accessdate=12 May 2012|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520153407/http://www.e-fanclub.com/kirafes2012/index_cart.asp|archivedate=20 May 2012}}</ref>\n*''Kiramune Special Book'' ''Kiramune's music label company 3rd year anniversary publication'' Tetsuya Kakihara&nbsp;\u2013 Released: April 2012<ref>{{Cite web|publisher=Kiramune |title= ''Kiramune Special Book'' Tetsuya Kakihara |url=http://www.ongakusenkasha.co.jp/pick-up/kiramune/index.html|accessdate=12 May 2012}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://zynchro.jp/talent/kakihara.html Official agency profile] {{in lang|ja}}\n*[http://kiramune.jp/artist/kakihara/ Kiramune profile&nbsp;\u2013 Tetsuya Kakihara] {{in lang|ja}}\n<!-- *[http://ameblo.jp/tetsuya-kakihara/ Tetsuya Kakihara's official blog (new one: Aug. 1, 2013~ )\u00a0\u2013 let go] {{in lang|ja}}\n*[http://kakiharatetsuya.cocolog-nifty.com/blog/ Tetsuya Kakihara's official blog (previous one: Aug. 1 2008 ~ Aug. 1, 2013)\u00a0\u2013 Next One] {{in lang|ja}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20130502162006/http://www.81produce.co.jp/list.cgi?man+1112518134330 Tetsuya Kakihara] at [[81 Produce]] (archive page on 2 May 2013) -->\n*[http://gph.sakura.ne.jp/va_memo/system/vadb.cgi?action=view_ind&value=00748&namecode=1 Tetsuya Kakihara] at GamePlaza-Haruka Voice Acting Database {{in lang|ja}}\n*[http://www.usagi.org/doi-bin/seiyuu-lookup.pl?DB=anime&value=Tetsuya+Kakihara&N= Tetsuya Kakihara] at Hitoshi Doi's Seiyuu Database\n*{{ann|people|28816}}\n*{{IMDb name|id=2132616}}\n\n{{Seiyu Award for Best Rookie Actor}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kakihara, Tetsuya}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]